No, go back to it.

00:08:17.380 --> 00:08:17.840
Go back to the last slide.

00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:22.450
LARRY NIVEN: Their minutes are
still 60 seconds longer.

00:08:22.450 --> 00:08:24.992
GREGORY BENFORD: This is from
Peter Nichols, a noted SF

00:08:24.992 --> 00:08:30.270
critic, who said, basically
it's an interesting--

00:08:30.270 --> 00:08:32.429
