00:08:45.535 --> 00:08:47.250
LARRY NIVEN: But it is
the amateurish--

00:08:47.250 --> 00:08:49.760
the semi-amateurish
way to write.

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:54.630
I knew I was young and foolish
and needed more skills.

00:08:54.630 --> 00:08:56.560
when I wrote "Ringworld."

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:57.510
GREGORY BENFORD: Right.

00:08:57.510 --> 00:08:58.980
This, by the way,
is from an essay

00:08:58.980 --> 00:09:00.870
that's on my own website.

00:09:00.870 --> 00:09:03.580
With Peter's permission, I put
the whole essay up about

00:09:03.580 --> 00:09:05.100
re-reading hard science
fiction.

00:09:05.100 --> 00:09:06.510
It's a lot of thoughts
about it.

